name: Tyson
description: Tyson, also known as “Mike Tyson” and “Mike Tyson OG”, is an indica weed strain made from a cross of unknown strains. Named after former undisputed heavyweight champion Mike Tyson, this strain is sure to knock you out. Bred by Canna Clinic, Tyson delivers a punch of indica effects known to fully relax the body while dulling pain, stress, insomnia, and appetite loss. Tyson is 20% THC, making this strain an ideal choice for experienced cannabis consumers. Leafly customers tell us Tyson effects include sleepy, relaxed, and hungry. Medical marijuana patients often choose Tyson when dealing with symptoms associated with insomnia, stress, and anxiety. Bred by Canna Clinic, Tyson features flavors like diesel, pungent, and skunk. The dominant terpene of this strain is myrcene. The average price of Tyson typically ranges from $10-$20 per gram. If you’re looking for a potent and soothing strain that can ease your mind and body, Tyson might be the perfect choice for you.
